And Then There Were 10: Ben discovers the Omnitrix.
Washington B.C.: Ben uses the Omnitrix to stop Dr. Animo.
The Krakken: Ben encounters a mysterious sea creature.
Permanent Retirement: Ben faces off against shape-shifting aliens.
Hunted: Ben fights against alien bounty hunters.
Tourist Trap: Ben battles a giant mutant rat.
Kevin 11: Ben meets Kevin, a kid with alien powers.
The Alliance: Ben must stop a mutated gang leader.
Last Laugh: Ben fights Zombozo and his clown minions.
Lucky Girl: Gwen gains magic powers from a charm.
A Small Problem: Ben shrinks down to a tiny size.
Side Effects: Ben fights aliens while battling a cold.
Secrets: Ben uncovers the secrets of the Omnitrix.
Truth: Ben discovers more about the Omnitrix.
The Big Tick: Ben encounters a dangerous alien.
Framed: Ben is framed for crimes by Kevin.
Gwen 10: Gwen takes the Omnitrix in an alternate timeline.

The Galactic Enforcers: Ben teams up with intergalactic heroes.
Camp Fear: Ben faces off against mutant plants.
Ultimate Weapon: Ben searches for a powerful ancient artifact.
Tough Luck: Ben battles a villain who can manipulate luck.
They Lurk Below: Ben fights a sea monster and discovers an underwater city.
Ghostfreaked Out: Ghostfreak returns to haunt Ben.
Dr. Animo and the Mutant Ray: Ben battles Dr. Animo's mutant creations.
Back with a Vengeance: Vilgax returns with Kevin for revenge on Ben.

Merry Christmas: Ben encounters a mysterious town trapped in an eternal Christmas.

Don't Drink the Water: Ben and Max turn into kids after being exposed to mystical water.

Ben 4 Good Buddy: Ben battles trucker aliens who steal valuable cargo.
Ready to Rumble: Ben enters an underground alien wrestling ring.
Ken 10: Ben meets his future son who struggles with the Omnitrix.
Ben 10 vs. Negative 10 (Part 1): Ben faces off against the Negative 10, a team of villains.
Ben 10 vs. Negative 10 (Part 2): The final battle with the Negative 10 unfolds.
Goodbye and Good Riddance: Ben returns to school after his summer adventures.
